        </item>
        <item>
            <title>MacBook Air M4 (2025) 搭載 M4 處理器，新「天藍色」+ 發售日期 + 售價、規格資訊</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/macbook-air-2025-m4/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=macbook-air-2025-m4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/macbook-air-2025-m4/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 14:28:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MacBook Air]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295797</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>繼早前 iPad Air, iPad 之後，Apple 在香港時間今晚再發佈新產品－－全新 MacBook Air 搭載 M4 晶片。新型號以 M4 晶片為核心，結合輕巧外型與長續航力，方便外出工作長期使用。今次 Apple 為手提電腦推出一款全新顏色「天藍色」，同樣提供 13 吋、15 吋型號，建議零售價由 HK$7,999 起，將於 3 月 12 日發售（現時接受預訂）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/hero_endframe__c67cz-1-694x319.png" alt="" width="694" height="319" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/hero_endframe__c67cz-1-694x319.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/hero_endframe__c67cz-1.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295829" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3.jpg 980w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這次 MacBook Air 更新了 M4 晶片，處理速度比上一代更快。晶片內的神經網絡引擎也對各類人工智慧功能有一定幫助，從視像通話的人物置中效果，到 AI 協助優化影像，甚至一些大型語言模型的運行，都能發揮更高效率。若本身已是 iPhone 用戶，把手機的資料或應用程式狀態直接帶到電腦上操作更為便利。無論是把 iPhone 上的文字直接複製貼到 MacBook Air，或利用 iCloud 同步照片、文件，兩者之間的銜接都十分順暢。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1295811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305102733-694x331.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="331" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305102733-694x331.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305102733-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MacBook Air 除搭載最新 M4 晶片，它最顯著的特點之一，是電池可使用至多 18 小時，配合支援快速充電的設計，能在短時間內回復過半電量，對於經常在路上或需要長時間使用電腦的人來説相當實用。此外，MacBook Air 採用無風扇設計，運行時保持安靜，從剪輯影片到開啟多個應用程式，整體表現都顯得流暢。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295804" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_side_skyblue_-1-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_side_skyblue_-1-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_side_skyblue_-1.jpg 1208w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295803" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_portability_1-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_portability_1-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_portability_1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在外型與顏色選擇上，新推出的天藍色為 MacBook Air 帶來不同於以往的風格，也保留了銀色、星光色及午夜暗色等選項。機身以再生鋁金屬製造，不僅耐用，還進一步展現了環保意識。無論是 13 吋抑或 15 吋型號，都維持輕薄設計，放進揹包後毫不笨重，帶著趴趴走不成問題。對於習慣一次處理多項工作的用家，15 吋螢幕所提供的額外視野更能提升效率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295805" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_right__-694x70.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="70" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_right__-694x70.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_right__.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_left__b-694x80.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="80" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_left__b-694x80.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_left__b.jpg 1276w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在顯示器方面，MacBook Air 採用 Liquid Retina 技術，能呈現逼真的色彩和細膩的對比度，文字也更清晰。配合高素質的三麥克風與音響設計，不論是視像會議或觀賞影片都能提供不錯的體驗。鏡頭具備人物置中與桌上視角等功能，開會或線上教學時更方便展示自己的作品或做示範。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295808" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101858-694x413.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="413" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101858-694x413.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101858-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295809" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101908-694x369.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101908-694x369.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101908-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295807" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_sizes_endfram-694x524.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="524" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_sizes_endfram-694x524.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_sizes_endfram.jpg 1192w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>擴充能力方面，MacBook Air 配備 MagSafe 充電線，可以輕鬆吸附在機身上並在需要時迅速脫落，避免被線纏住或扯跌。兩個 Thunderbolt 4 連接埠則能連接高速配件或外置顯示器，且 Wi‑Fi 6E 帶來更快的無線網絡速度。在安全性上，Touch ID 功能可快速解鎖電腦，或進行購物及付款授權，操作俐落又安全。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295801" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_magsafe_skybl-694x373.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_magsafe_skybl-694x373.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_magsafe_skybl.jpg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Apple 也在這款電腦中加入了 Apple Intelligence 功能，讓用家在寫文章或整理圖片時，能更輕鬆地進行校對、編修，或利用大型模型產生各式創意圖像。值得一提的是，系統非常重視使用者私隱，利用 Mac 上的裝置端處理技術和私密雲端運算，力求保護個人資料安全。</p><h2>售價與供應</h2><div dir="auto">13 吋$7,999 起</div><div dir="auto">15 吋$9,499 起</div><div dir="auto">立即可預訂，3 月 12 日發售</div><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
